{"tid":1068882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿狗敢唔敢挑機 (2)","createTime":"2019-03-19T14:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T17:36:10.000Z","uid":153600,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"78dad8765ecefa06162e7579657714f0605d8dd9","tid":1068882,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"聽晚阿仙奴晉級歐聯，呀唔係，係歐霸既<br />\n<br />\n我即捐$5000俾無國界醫生，兼認阿狗做契爺，兼永遠退出體育台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前題只係阿狗下個po topic唔好再提曼聯空難<br />\n<br />\n老實講，我個人就唔介意講曼聯空難，因為真心冇感覺，純粹想略盡綿力維護一下球會尊嚴，因為我地唔係狗黎，狗先唔需要尊嚴<br />\n<br />\n好似阿狗咁d戰績/冠軍數俾人笑到面都黃，都可以扮冇野笑騎騎一齊笑埋一份，一條心做死狗，冇人覺得恥辱既，呢d咪阿狗迷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n契弟找數喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3543a8cfb316acc6838a663c79d7e28f8232a64b","tid":1068882,"uid":30306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"紅魔謎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6664bb8d4249ae5791a6771791de5ca1fb4381","tid":1068882,"uid":141862,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"會員編號#169<br />\n全家死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba20dad83627fc83210b6e3504a2b93dea758d09","tid":1068882,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb6664bb8d4249ae5791a6771791de5ca1fb4381","tid":1068882,"uid":141862,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"會員編號#169<br />\n全家死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl