贈俾佢，當係佢愛隊幫佢做左少少野<br />\n<br />\n其他野就一筆勾銷？咁樣處理好似比較好<br />\n大家和解<br />\n<br />\ndeal就留個銀行戶口/馬會戶口係度，我會入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係 當初諗住型下先咁講，我平時旗都唔會買<br />\n我對慈善機構好反感既<br />\n<br />\n不過輸就係輸左，5000想用返係d實在d既地方，希望果位巴打會留戶口啦，真找數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿迷自己唔要咋，唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6hucps.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6hucps.png&h=d4957855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享單笑料俾你地聽下。<br />\n<br />\n話說琴晚我收到og巴個戶口就出左去禁錢入數架喇，跟住點知俾佢fake左，既然禁左出黎我就唔想收返，隔離有間馬會，我就入左去點指兵兵買左場波，我平時就唔賭既，馬會戶口都冇申請，就求其簡左場2倍買落去，諗住中左就派一萬睇下佢要唔要<br />\n<br />\n而家場波就輸左既，捐左6000俾馬會幫我做善事啦<br />\n<br />\n你地話我賴又好乜都好啦，可以對返個時間，買波個時間就係我琴晚諗住入數既時間黎<br />\n<br />\n當笑料睇又好乜都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢d預左派既錢輸都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959dfe8f32ab78fa3582e3bdd53409cbd7a4fe19","tid":1068882,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c5550d366c120ae71475b70f2834409266a6cdf","tid":1068882,"uid":137406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"咪咁懶 整埋整合包<br />\nCap哂隻空難狗d柒野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"岩岩cap左D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94982471e5b5898039218cb685b4be243c9e48f1","tid":1068882,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baa6a2dc81ad7ed8e4f99d35112207784f558e9b","tid":1068882,"uid":153600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"契弟所有柒事回顧 : <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okuXLq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FokuXLq8.jpg&h=2d2f580f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tXWSzju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F